# CODEOWNERS — defines who must approve pull requests.
#
# Every PR requires approval from the repository owner before it can be merged.
# GitHub enforces this automatically when branch protection is enabled.
#
# To enable: GitHub → Settings → Branches → Add rule for main/stage/dev
#   ✅ Require a pull request before merging
#   ✅ Require approvals: 1
#   ✅ Require review from Code Owners
#   ✅ Require status checks to pass (add: backend-ci, frontend-ci, pr-gate)
#   ✅ Do not allow bypassing the above settings

